Subject: Nerdcore is Dead(?)
Description: Nerdcore hip-hop is often taken as a parody genre.  With 'nerdy' references sneaking into more and more mainstream music, is 'nerd rap' a stale term?  Join some of the top artists as they debate the validity of their own genre.
